                      </p>
                      
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card mb-4 mb-md-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <p class="mb-4"><span class="text-primary font-italic me-1">Products</span> 
